<section class="pg-section" data-section="What To Expect During Your 60-Minute Cupping Facial Experience">
  <h2 class="pg-h">What To Expect During Your 60-Minute Cupping Facial Experience</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">Every step is designed for your comfort and results. Here's exactly what happens during your 60-minute treatment at our Millburn spa.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Consultation &amp; Skin Assessment (5-10 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Your treatment begins with a thorough consultation to understand your skin goals and concerns. Our expert esthetician analyzes your facial structure and skin condition to customize the cupping technique and pressure for optimal results.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Deep Cleansing &amp; Preparation (10-15 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Your skin is thoroughly cleansed to remove makeup, oils, and impurities. We apply a special facial oil that allows the cups to glide smoothly across your skin while providing the perfect seal for effective suction therapy.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Therapeutic Cupping Treatment (35-40 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Using specialized facial cups of various sizes, we create gentle suction to lift and massage different areas of your face and neck. The cups are moved in specific patterns to target sagging areas, improve circulation, and stimulate natural lifting. You'll feel a gentle pulling sensation that most clients find deeply relaxing.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Finishing Treatment &amp; Aftercare (5-10 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">We complete your treatment with a nourishing serum application and gentle facial massage to maximize absorption. You'll receive personalized aftercare instructions to maintain your lifted, glowing results.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">Completely Comfortable &amp; Safe</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">The cupping process feels like a gentle, rhythmic pulling sensation that most clients find deeply relaxing and therapeutic. There's no pain, just a unique massage-like feeling that leaves you refreshed and rejuvenated.</p>
</section>

